metadata.name: Z's Ritual
metadata.description:
Silence and thoughts...  
Your silhouette was running around in my head. I needed a memory to make myself happy. I was listening to a lullaby in the background. I rewound and listened to it again, a music that accompanied my ritual. My picture was being drawn in rhythm with the music. And I was waiting, wishing that this dream I had seen with my eyes open would come true.
